text: Jean-Louis Martin (born 20 August 1939) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Landes (department)
